videos.description: Stetson Bennett runs around the defenders and finds a clear path to the end zone for a 2-yard Georgia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bennett finds an opening for short Georgia TD) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bennett finds an opening for short Georgia TD

videos.description: Zamir White runs into traffic, but breaks through and goes straight into the end zone for a 22-yard Bulldogs touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Georgia's White takes off for 22-yard TD run) 2020/10/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia's White takes off for 22-yard TD run

videos.description: Quarterback Stetson Bennett credits the Kentucky defense and says the UGA offense played well "other than two throws" in a 14-3 victory.
videos.headline: Bennett says Dawgs' offense plenty good enough vs. UK

videos.description: Kirby Smart says second-teamers had to step up on defense while the rushing attack was the key for the Bulldogs' offense against Kentucky.
videos.headline: Georgia's defense, rushing attack allow Smart to smile

videos.description: In a defense-oriented matchup, the No. 5 Dawgs put up enough offense (346 total yards) to beat the Wildcats 14-3 on the road.
videos.headline: Georgia slips past Kentucky in low-scoring contest
